{
  "stem": "24163.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he and my mother, who worked in the office, they were hardworking people, both of them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and as I said, he had built up a good business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, this man who came in, appointed by the Nazi, with a big swastika always on his lapel-- he wore it every morning when he came in-- his name was Novak.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he ran my father's business, in as much as-- particularly the accounts receivables.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He saw to it that they were channeled into different funds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And slowly, but surely, my father's business was choked, more and more, because he continued to work in a-- on a limit-- more limited basis.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the monies that were due him, or the monies that came in, were actually stolen from him by this Novak, on behalf of the German government, the Nazi party, whatever.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That happened to many businesses owned by German-Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's-- towards the end, there probably was very little left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it did him-- did him little good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] You could protest, and I'm sure he did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He raised his voice probably more than once.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you had to be careful, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This-- these-- the-- the laws were doctored, doctored so this became law.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- very heavy extra taxes were leveled against the German-Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all these things were then, so-called, quote unquote, lawful in the eyes of the German Nazi government.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they just simply drained the business, until, more or less, towards the end, there was very little left of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I remember, maybe not April 1, I remember Hitler's birthday, April 30th, 1933.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why do I remember that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived in an apartment, a lovely-- we had just a new building we had moved into.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a sun parlor.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
